the first time, in front of Sleeping Beauty Castle. ; Photo, Mae Dewey, 95, of 
the San Carlos Reservation was the oldest of the Apache group. ; Photo, Mickey 
plants a mouse-kiss on park visitor Louise Dewey. GAIL FISHER / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
