<HEAD>No Relief From Arctic Blast</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: INSERTS 4 grafs after 7th graf, `In Nevada ..., to UPDATE with
state offices closing in New Mexico, police urging people to rescue
drunks in snow, power outage in Wyoming; ADDS 1 graf to UPDATE with
